    {
      "segment_id": "seg_013",
      "text": "Hindi, okay. This is related to your insurance policy. We have planned to proceed with your proposal, but before that, we need to conduct a video call telephonic medical verification. In this, I will ask you some questions related to your medical history and some verification questions, okay?",
      "speaker": "doctor",
