      "start_timestamp": "00:48",
      "end_timestamp": "00:49"
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "seg_015",
      "text": "Please pay attention, whatever answers you give me about your health, about your habits, are part of this insurance application. If it gets accepted, a legal contract will be formed between you and the company. If any of your answers turn out to be false or do not match later, it will directly affect your policy. The policy can be canceled even before being issued, and it can also be rejected after being issued. So please answer carefully, correctly, and completely.",
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "start_timestamp": "00:50",
      "end_timestamp": "01:18"
    },
    {
